{"tid":1926984,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【抵制TVB週日任】繼續打擊myTV SUPER伙伴 - 狙擊HGC寬頻 (15 Mar)","createTime":"2020-03-15T13:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T10:15:13.000Z","uid":267969,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"79f143a6625463ea890941e175496cd8203cfe72","tid":1926984,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:10:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />週日特別任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />15 Mar 2020】</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTxRWpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTxRWpG.jpg&h=ac2ec52b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">解約</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">所有戰士：去派嬲兼留言！</span></strong><br />\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/HGCbroadband/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHGCbroadband%2F&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyU9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=2cf0293c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/HGCbroadband/</a></strong></span><br />\n留言Template:<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(客戶)</span></strong><br />\n我用HGC寬頻上網係為咗接收全面資訊，而唔係俾錢你用嚟支持無綫電視假新聞，貴公司服務綑綁myTV SUPER，我決定完約後正式轉台！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(非客戶)</span></strong><br />\n你唔結束myTV SUPER綑綁式服務，我決定一世唔用HGC</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">HGC客戶：Cut服務！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就算你唔拎個盒，廢老都會拎，集體終止服務先可以對公司造成壓力！</span>😡<br />\n👉🏻<strong>致電客戶熱線1223索取終止服務表格</strong>，並於終止服務日最少一個月前(但不多於兩個月) 將已填妥之表格<br />\n💢註明取消原因係「唔滿意myTV SUPER綑綁式服務」<br />\n<br />\n📃【背景】<br />\n👉🏻 myTV SUPER 總用戶127萬，為TVB全年賺1.82億🤬<br />\n👉🏻 HGC新客戶一定包埋myTV SUPER廢盒🤢"},{"pid":"c3152c01dd91a507955f3584cdd5dff32a634856","tid":1926984,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfee9fba008a4ca9e298a684f884d6c3357ca8a0","tid":1926984,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babc8fc0665190b93ed366856b9a59b96b51092c","tid":1926984,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fb5ce7d7b4581bdb411d0fb6132a5f39e651e4","tid":1926984,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"15e74214c3df9bf42b94cd6ad979e2976a2dded6","tid":1926984,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cede0f15142ec08246e4b2bca507a1ec4f9e81","tid":1926984,"uid":245044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:16:57.000Z","msg":"PISH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33acca163e22f4730349f2d0ac4b2d2dd3d695ef","tid":1926984,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:17:19.000Z